        <div style="width:100%; min-height: 400px;">
            <h2 style="color:#000033;">The International Dietetic Internship in Community Nutrition: </h2>
            <p>
                This is an innovative 4-week training programme in community nutrition for dietetic interns.
                Students from three universities (i.e., Iowa State University â€“ USA, McGill University - Canada and
                the University of Ghana) participate in this program. The program is offered twice a year:
            <ul style="color:#000033;">
                <li> May/June</li>
                <li>October/November</li>
            </ul>
            This program brings together dietetic interns from Ghana and North America to use the nutritional care processes in examining the nutritional problems of the inhabitants in selected rural communities.
            The first training program was run in May 2012. To date we have organized many successful rotations and is currently
            preparing to host another on ,<span class="w3-text-red"> <%= data.trainingDate %> </span>.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


<div class="w3-row-padding w3-light-gray" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap;">

    <div class="w3-half" style="flex-grow: 1; margin: 27px 0px; flex-basis:450px ">

